<h3>append</h3>

<p>Appends selected elements from loaded page to the container.</p>

<div class="duo example">
  <div class="duo__cell example__code">
    ``` js
    append: '.post',
    // append .post elements from next page to container
    ```
  </div>
  <div class="duo__cell example__demo">
