<h2>UI</h2>

{{! ----------------------------------------------------------------- }}

<h3>hideNav</h3>

<p>Hides navigation element.</p>

``` html
<!-- hide pagination with infinite scroll enabled -->
<div class="pagination">
  <span class="pagination__current">Page 1</span>
  <a class="pagination__next" href="/page/2">Next</a>
</div>
```

``` js
hideNav: '.pagination',
```

